- Alright, you think about it.
- I will.

17:39.957 --> 17:42.507
It's hard to be mad at you,
Coach Taylor.

17:44.889 --> 17:47.839
- It's good to see you.
- You'll be thinking about what I said.

17:47.959 --> 17:50.210
- Yes, ma'am.
- Alright, bye-bye.

17:55.132 --> 17:56.577
Hey guys, good news, I got the...

18:01.774 --> 18:04.836
- Did you get the permits?
- What the hell is going on, here?

18:04.997 --> 18:07.880
I'm just improvising, man.
Just look, look. Bigger, uh?

18:10.252 --> 18:13.010
- Man, that is the Cadillac of toilets.
- Yeah, check it out.

18:13.697 --> 18:14.887
- Bidet.
- Bidet?

18:15.048 --> 18:17.618
- Right here. Bidet.
- Cleans your butt.

18:17.738 --> 18:19.017
$1,700?

18:19.642 --> 18:21.394
You spent $1,700 on a toilet?

